aa(lp42
VThese bacteria are not passive riders,
p43
aVthese are incredibly important, they keep us alive.
p44
aVThey cover us in an invisible body armor
p45
aVthat keeps environmental insults out
p46
aVso that we stay healthy.
p47
aVThey digest our food, they make our vitamins,
p48
aVthey actually educate your immune system
p49
aVto keep bad microbes out.
p50
aVSo they do all these amazing things
p51
aVthat help us and are vital for keeping us alive,
p52
aVand they never get any press for that.
p53
aVBut they get a lot of press because they do a lot of
p54
aVterrible things as well.
p55
aVSo, there's all kinds of bacteria on the Earth
p56
aVthat have no business being in you or on you at any time,
p57
