aa(lp233
VOnce we got that far we thought
p234
aVwe were starting to understand that bacteria have these social behaviors.
p235
aVBut what we were really thinking about is that most of the time
p236
aVbacteria don't live by themselves, they live in incredible mixtures,
p237
