aa(lp248
VSo we went back to molecular biology
p249
aVand started studying different bacteria,
p250
aVand what we've found now is that
p251
aVin fact, bacteria are multilingual.
p252
aVThey all have a species-specific system \u2014
p253
aVthey have a molecule that says "me."
p254
